    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The CUBE》是一款多人角色扮演射击游戏，完美融合了别具匠心的世界设定、引人入胜的剧情故事和激动人心的任务目标。在这个生机勃勃的世界中，你将邂逅个性鲜明的角色，探索丰富多样的生物群系，迎战数不胜数的敌人与实力强大的boss。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230430/extras/35f8f098fada863ef71a8e2359651d04.avif?t=1751886340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230430/extras_big/35f8f098fada863ef71a8e2359651d04.avif?t=1751886340 width=800 height=398 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230430/extras/89fb05bd6c02f2d595ff229b8ffd9daf.poster.avif?t=1751886340\" width=800 height=522 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230430/extras/89fb05bd6c02f2d595ff229b8ffd9daf.webm?t=1751886340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230430/extras/89fb05bd6c02f2d595ff229b8ffd9daf.mp4?t=1751886340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230430/extras/ce27fcf30fc95c2e624e2e2ea1420bd3.avif?t=1751886340\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230430/extras_big/ce27fcf30fc95c2e624e2e2ea1420bd3.avif?t=1751886340 width=800 height=392 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230430/extras/b5adb29c0dacaf7ecd865b128d77df37.poster.avif?t=1751886340\" width=800 height=522 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230430/extras/b5a